{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And we see in the fireworks' light, a young MAN in his early 30s, THOMAS BUTTON, running up to the gate of a fashionable town home.
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He nearly collides with a PRIEST who arrives there at the same time.
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Thomas runs past him, up the steps...
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 20 INT. BUTTON HOUSE, NEW ORLEANS - NIGHT 1918
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...He runs past a solemn Maid and up a long staircase... barging into the MASTER BEDROOM...
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 10.
