{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... where we see a young Woman is lying on a bloody bed, frantically being administered to by a DOCTOR with the help of the small domestic staff... the PRIEST enters...
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THOMAS BUTTON
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {META_DATA}: (seeing him)
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {DIALOGUE}: Why are you here?
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THE DOCTOR
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {DIALOGUE}: Thomas, I'm afraid she's not going to survive...
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And the Priest bends to say last rites over the pretty young woman... and the maids, bringing bedsheets, futilely start to change her bloody linens...
{0:8:8 - 0:8:58} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THOMAS BUTTON
{0:8:54 - 0:8:58} {DIALOGUE}: That's enough...!
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {DIALOGUE}: All of you!
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They move out of the way... and Thomas kneels beside his wife... She's pale white, fear in her soft brown eyes... He takes her hand...
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THOMAS BUTTON (CONT'D)
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {DIALOGUE}: I came as quickly as I could... I'm sorry I took so long, the streets are filled with people...
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As if to underscore it, fireworks go off...
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THOMAS BUTTON (CONT'D)
{0:8:54 - 0:9:5} {DIALOGUE}: You are going to be alright, my dearest darling... I will not let anything happen to you...
