{0:13:1 - 0:13:10} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There's a myriad of old dark rooms... heavy furniture and carpets... an eclectic mixture of the possessions of those who have lived and died here over many years... and we see a parlor is crowded with Old People, from sixty to ninety-five, in various stages of health... various contraptions to keep them "afloat".
{0:13:1 - 0:13:10} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An Old Age Home.
