{0:14:9 - 0:14:43} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 27 INT. PARLOR, NOLAN HOUSE, NEW ORLEANS - NIGHT, 1918
{0:14:9 - 0:14:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We see the Doctor, an older man in a tired suit, who has done this longer than he cares to remember, finishing examining one of the elderly boarders.
