{0:18:37 - 0:19:18} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A line of old people in rockers.
{0:18:37 - 0:19:18} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Benjamin, like any six- year-old, bored, wheels his chair back and forth, between them... until one of the oldsters, who has had enough, sticks his cane in the spokes of his wheelchair, making him come to an abrupt stop... Benjamin, sitting with the other oldsters on the porch... the old people rocking... Sounds drift from the street beyond the wall... children playing... people talking...
