{0:22:39 - 0:23:5} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A sweltering shout 'em up Negro gospel tent.
{0:22:39 - 0:23:5} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Queenie pushes Benjamin in his wheelchair past a line of people looking to be healed, bringing him face to face with a mountain of a PREACHER, pouring sweat and full of fire...
{0:22:39 - 0:23:5} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THE PREACHER
