{0:36:25 - 0:36:27} {DIALOGUE}: Now, you come back to bed, young lady...!
{0:36:27 - 0:36:31} {DIALOGUE}: You're too young to be wandering around in the night by yourself...
{0:36:27 - 0:36:37} {META_DATA}: (and a last word to Benjamin)
{0:36:33 - 0:36:37} {DIALOGUE}: You should be ashamed of yourself!
