{0:36:33 - 0:36:55} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There's a slight sound and he sees Queenie, in her nightgown, standing in the doorway...
{0:36:33 - 0:36:55} {CHARACTER_NAME}: QUEENIE
{0:36:53 - 0:36:55} {DIALOGUE}: You are a different child... a man child.
{0:36:57 - 0:37:1} {DIALOGUE}: People aren't going to understand how different you are.
