{0:37:7 - 0:37:10} {DIALOGUE}: What's wrong with me, Mother?
{0:37:7 - 0:37:17} {CHARACTER_NAME}: QUEENIE
{0:37:14 - 0:37:17} {DIALOGUE}: God hasn't said yet.
{0:37:21 - 0:37:25} {DIALOGUE}: Now, back to bed and behave yourself.
