{0:55:6 - 0:55:11} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He's quiet, he hadn't thought of that...
{0:55:6 - 0:55:11} {CHARACTER_NAME}: THE WOMAN (CONT'D)
{0:55:9 - 0:55:11} {DIALOGUE}: That would be an awful responsibility...
{0:55:9 - 0:55:15} {CHARACTER_NAME}: BENJAMIN BUTTON'S (V.O.)
{0:55:11 - 0:55:15} {DIALOGUE}: I had never thought about life or death that way before...
