{1:0:28 - 1:0:46} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CAPT. MIKE (CONT'D)
{1:0:28 - 1:0:46} {DIALOGUE}: wit' movin' pictures, you know what it showed, they wing tips are doin' dis...
{1:0:28 - 1:0:46} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And he draws on a napkin a FIGURE EIGHT...
{1:0:28 - 1:0:46} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CAPT. MIKE (CONT'D)
{1:0:42 - 1:0:46} {DIALOGUE}: Does you know what the figure- eight is the mathematical symbol of...?!
{1:0:42 - 1:0:50} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Pointing at the symbol...
{1:0:42 - 1:0:50} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CAPT. MIKE (CONT'D)
{1:0:49 - 1:0:50} {DIALOGUE}: Infinity!
{1:0:49 - 1:1:2} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And for some drunken reason, no matter what language they might speak, they all laugh...
{1:0:49 - 1:1:2} {CHARACTER_NAME}: BENJAMIN BUTTON'S (V.O.)
{1:0:58 - 1:1:2} {DIALOGUE}: Everybody, no matter what differences they had, the languages, the color of their skin, had one thing in common... they were drunk every single night...
{1:0:58 - 1:1:14} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then there's a shout -- and as if to underscore things, the Brody twins are kicking the shit out of each other again...
