{1:11:15 - 1:13:22} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Daisy's answer for her is...
{1:11:15 - 1:13:22} {CHARACTER_NAME}: DAISY
{1:11:15 - 1:13:22} {DIALOGUE}: It must have been very cold.
{1:13:16 - 1:13:22} {DIALOGUE}: I'm glad he had somebody to keep him warm.
