{1:13:16 - 1:13:28} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CAROLINE
{1:13:16 - 1:13:28} {META_DATA}: (after a beat, reading)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:28} {DIALOGUE}: "I couldn't wait to see her again."
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 83A.
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 125 INT. "WINTER PALACE," RUSSIA - ANOTHER LATE NIGHT, 1941
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Benjamin comes hurrying down the stairs.
