{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: BENJAMIN
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {META_DATA}: (self-conscious)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {DIALOGUE}: I'm not dressed --
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ELIZABETH ABBOTT
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {DIALOGUE}: You're delicious just as you are...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She laughs, taking his arm, walking to the dining room as if going to dinner... They sit at a table... which she has set for them... Caviar and Vodka...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ELIZABETH ABBOTT (CONT'D)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {DIALOGUE}: Don't bother with the cheese or the wine here, they're quite common... but the caviar and the vodka are plentiful and sublime...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She feeds him a spoonful of the caviar...Unaccustomed to it, he swallows it too quickly...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ELIZABETH ABBOTT (CONT'D)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {DIALOGUE}: Take your time... If you eat it all at once there will be nothing left to enjoy... savor it...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She gives him another spoonful... and takes one herself... He takes his time... They both do... savoring it...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ELIZABETH ABBOTT (CONT'D)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {META_DATA}: (pouring)
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {DIALOGUE}: Now, a swallow of vodka...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Which they do... She laughs... Looking at him...
{1:13:25 - 1:13:43} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ELIZABETH ABBOTT (CONT'D)
