{1:16:21 - 1:16:24} {DIALOGUE}: We's goin' to war, gentlemen!
{1:16:21 - 1:16:33} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And filled with fervor, they give a cheer.
{1:16:21 - 1:16:33} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 139 INT. BENJAMIN'S ROOM, "WINTER PALACE" LATER, 1941
{1:16:21 - 1:16:33} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Benjamin unlocking the door to his room.
