{1:16:31 - 1:16:33} {DIALOGUE}: She had left a note.
{1:16:34 - 1:16:37} {DIALOGUE}: She wrote, "it was nice to have met you."
{1:16:34 - 1:16:46} {DIALOGUE}: That was it.
{1:16:34 - 1:16:46} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And as he stands holding the letter in his room at the small Russian hotel:
{1:16:34 - 1:16:46} {CHARACTER_NAME}: BENJAMIN BUTTON'S (V.O.)
{1:16:34 - 1:16:46} {DIALOGUE}: And so, I went to war.
