{1:19:7 - 1:19:54} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CAPT. MIKE
{1:19:7 - 1:19:54} {META_DATA}: (mad as hell)
{1:19:51 - 1:19:54} {DIALOGUE}: We can't run from the fucker and we can't hide...!
