{1:34:38 - 1:35:13} {CHARACTER_NAME}: DAISY
{1:34:38 - 1:35:13} {DIALOGUE}: Do you think you are too old for me... I've been with older men...
{1:34:38 - 1:35:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And when he still doesn't respond... Daisy, rejected, takes up her shoes... And she starts off... Benjamin coming beside her... but they're not really walking together anymore... and the time for them, this time, has gone away...
{1:34:38 - 1:35:13} {CHARACTER_NAME}: BENJAMIN BUTTON'S (V.0.)
{1:34:38 - 1:35:13} {DIALOGUE}: You only get so many chances to be with someone... I let her go... and I missed it...
