{2:4:8 - 2:4:18} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 216 INT. HOTEL ROOM, THE CARIBBEAN HOTEL - NIGHT, 1963
{2:4:8 - 2:4:18} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A white hotel room... The storm shutters closed... The wind and the rain banging at the shutters... Daisy and Benjamin lying together on a bed out of the storm... She touches his face as if for the first time...
